"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=world+news+site:kyivindependent.com","Ukraine wouldn't launch Operation Spiderweb if Russia agreed to ceasefire, Zelensky says","https://kyivindependent.com/ukraine-wouldnt-launch-operation-spiderweb-if-russia-agreed-to-ceasefire-zelensky-says/","Thu, 05 Jun 2025 07:18:45 GMT","


