"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=world+news+site:kyivindependent.com","Ukraine strikes Russian missile base in Bryansk Oblast, damages Iskander launchers, Ukrainian military says","https://kyivindependent.com/ukraine-strikes-russian-missile-base-in-bryansk-oblast-damages-iskander-launchers-ukrainian-military-says/","Thu, 05 Jun 2025 09:36:16 GMT","


