"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=us+national+news+site:foxnews.com","Ricketts, Fetterman team up for crackdown on China's attempts to purchase US farmland","https://www.foxnews.com/politics/ricketts-fetterman-team-up-crackdown-chinas-attempts-purchase-us-farmland","Thu, 05 Jun 2025 16:00:00 GMT","


