"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=women's+us+soccer","U.S. U-23 Women's National Team captures 2-1 victory over Germany","https://www.soccerwire.com/news/u-s-u-23-womens-national-team-captures-2-1-victory-over-germany/","Thu, 05 Jun 2025 14:39:24 GMT","

