"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=site:indiewire.com","What Could Possibly Get ‘Ferris Bueller' Star Mia Sara Back to Acting After a Decade Off? Mike Flanagan Calling Her Bluff","https://www.indiewire.com/features/interviews/mia-sara-back-to-acting-life-of-chuck-1235129414/","Thu, 05 Jun 2025 15:00:00 GMT","

By providing your information, you agree to our Terms of Use and our Privacy Policy.
